text:
Why so important? ~1/3 of #immunosuppressed #patients esp those with #transplants, make no #antibody (& poss no Tcell) response to #CovidVaccine despite multiple doses. So remain unprotected & for some (on tac, low eGFR) the only treatment pre admission no longer works well
5/n
